dct_title_s: Insurance maps of the Palisades of lower Bergen County, New Jersey : comprising Edgewater, Fairview, Cliffside Park, Ridgefield, Fort Lee, Leonia and Palisades Park
dct_description_sm: Includes key, streets and specials index, and text. "3403." Historic Maps has sheets 47 and 74-76 of Palisades, N.J. series, showing Palisades Park.
